---
title: Mushroom Freekeh Bowl with Goat Cheese and Warm Balsamic Dressing
description: Warm up with this hearty winter freekeh bowl! Pan roasted mushrooms with balsamic and creamy goat cheese bring a robust and zesty flavour to this dish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mushroom-freekeh-bowl-df95e280.jpg
